Package com.marklogic.semantics.rdf4j.client

Contains classes that abstract the connection to MarkLogic Java Client API and attendant result and write caches.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MarkLogicClientDependent
    Common interface for objects that are dependent on MarkLogicClient.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MarkLogicClient
    An internal class that straddles Rdf4j and MarkLogic Java client API.
    TripleCache
    Timer implements write cache for efficient adding of triples.
    TripleDeleteCache
    Delete cache to optimize performance by batching the requests.
    TripleWriteCache
    Write cache to optimize performance by batching the requests.
